<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681289>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Arctosa costenola sp. nov. Male pedipalp holotype (ICN-Ar 1378) a–c (a, anterior; b, ventral; c, retrolateral). Scale bars: a–c, 0.25 mm. CMS cymbial macrosetae, DMA depression of median apophysis, E embolus, Pa posterior arm, Pp palea protuberance, Ra retrolateral arm, ST subtegulum, T tegulum, TA terminal apophysis" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681289/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681291>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Arctosa costenola sp. nov. Male pedipalp (ICN-Ar 1378) a–c (a, prolateral; b, ventral; c, retrolateral). Pedipalp bulb d–h (d, prolateral; e, ventral; f, retrolateral; g posterior; h, anterior). i dorsal cymbium macrosetae. Scale bars: a–c, 0.20 mm, d–h, 100 µm, i, 200 µm. C conductor, DMA depression of median apophysis, E embolus, Ra retrolateral arm, Pa posterior arm, T tegulum, TA terminal apophysis, TK tegular keel, ST subtegulum," ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681291/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681293>
    dc:description "FIGURE14. Arctosacostenola sp. nov. Femaleepigynum (ICN-Ar12745) a–d(a,ventral;b, dorsal;c, anterior;d, posterolateral). Scale bars: a–d, 0.25 mm. FD fertilization duct, H hood, HS head of spermatheca, MS median septum, SS stalk of spermatheca, VC vulval chamber." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681293/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681295>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Arctosa costenola sp. nov. Male habitus (ICN-Ar 1378) a, d, g–h (a, dorsal; d, ventral; g, lateral; h, frontal). Epigynum (ICN-Ar 12745) b, e (b, ventral; e, dorsal). Female habitus (ICN-Ar 12745) c, f, i (c, dorsal; f, ventral; i, lateral) Scale bars: a, d, g, 1 mm, b, e, 0.1 mm, h, 500 µm, c, f, i, 2 mm. H, hood, HS head of spermatheca, MS median septum, SS stalk of spermatheca, TS transversal septum, VC vulval chamber." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681295/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681297>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Arctosa costenola sp. nov. Male. Pedipalpal bulb SEM (ICN-Ar 1378) a–c (a, ventral; b, retrolateral details, c, detail of Pa). Scale bars: a, 150 µm, b–c, 50 µm. E embolus, MA median apophysis, Pa posterior arm, Ra retrolateral arm, ST subtegulum, T tegulum, TA Terminal apophysis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681297/files/figure.png" ;
